(7,'VatS 63',52,'Capp.Sist. 63',3,81,223,'Messen, Magnificats, Motetten','http://www.diamm.ac.uk/jsp/Descriptions?op=SOURCE&sourceKey=1481',0,'Copied in Rome, for use by Cappella Sistina. French heraldry probably connected with visit of King Charles VIII to Rome in 1495 (SherrPC).',1),
