(10,'VatS 42',52,'Capp.Sist. 42',1,81,NULL,'Passionen, Motetten','http://www.diamm.ac.uk/jsp/Descriptions?op=SOURCE&sourceKey=1474',0,'Copied in Rome, for use by Cappella Sistina. Ca. 1503-12 (SherrPM), with additions and revisions in first half of 16th century (DeanS); date 1507 on f. 154 is later addition, and may refer to date of composition of Carpentras Salve regina rather than date of copy.',1),
